President Muhammadu Buhari has felicitated with Governor Gboyega Oyetola of Osun State on the occasion of his 65th birthday. His message was contained in a statement on Sunday by presidential spokesman, Femi Adesina. “President Buhari joins the Oyetola family, friends and people of goodwill in wishing the governor good health, sound mind and more years of purposeful and visionary leadership for the good people of Osun State”, it read. “The President commends Governor Oyetola for his determination to improve infrastructure, social services, human and capital development in the State, urging him to execute all the programs of the All Progressives Congress (APC), and fulfill his campaign promises to the electorate. “President Buhari charges the governor to use the special occasion of his 65th anniversary as another privileged opportunity to rededicate himself to do more service to God and humanity.” Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.